    <div class="modal fade" id="nut" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            Nutrition Month Celebration
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/nutrition.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            The Nutrition Month celebration aims to mitigate the poor health conditions of many young people whose food preference include
            junk food, sugar-laden drinks and fat saturated fast food and street food products. Poor health is a major problem
            in the development of a strong and productive work force.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal fade" id="int" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            Investiture of Scouts, Indoor Camping for Grades 4-6
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/int.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            Investiture Ceremony is one of the most important ceremonies in Scouting. It marks the formal acceptance of the boys in the
            movement after they have completed the requirements of membership and have fully understood its essence. It gives
            them the thrill of belonging to a group and makes them feel ready to face new responsibilities.</p>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal fade" id="bw" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            Buwan ng Wika
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/buwan.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            Linguistics or the scientific study of language is greatly influenced by history, culture, social and political factors around
            the world. Here in the Philippines, the month of August is designated as Buwan ng Wika, which is celebrated month-long
            to promote the national language. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal fade" id="camp" role="dialog">
