          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/hscamping.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            Indoor camping activities are yearly done with the following objectives:
            </br>
            • To improve social skills
            </br>
            • To provide new and positive experiences
            </br>
            • To build independence and ability to operate on their own or with different people.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="modal fade" id="cgw" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
