            Career Guidance Week
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/cgw.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            During the Career Guidance Week, the school intensifies the conduct of awareness campaigns, career fairs, and orientation
            activities on the Senior High School program. During this period, an offline search facility shall be made accessible
            in the computer laboratories and terminals, wherein students can browse through the menu of track offerings as
            well as their respective programs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="modal fade" id="un" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            United Nations Celebration
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/un.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">

            United Nations Day is celebrated every October 24 in honor of the intergovernmental organization promoting human rights,
            social progress, and world peace. Here at PBCSSI, United Nations Day is celebrated by having students dress up
            in the national costumes or traditional clothing of different nations, and holding lessons about cultural diversity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="smc" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            Scie-Math Celebration
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/sciemathweek.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">
            Science Week is an annual national celebration of the life-changing and fascinating worlds of science, technology, engineering
            and mathematics. The celebration highlights how science, technology and engineering are fundamental to everyday
            life, and demonstrate their importance to the future of our society and economy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="sr" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog modal-m">
