          <div class="modal-header" style="padding: 3%">
            Spiritual Retreats for Graduating Students
          </div>
          <img style="padding: 3%; border-radius: 30px;" src="images/activities/spiritualretreat.png " class="img-responsive" alt="">
          <p style="padding: 3%">
            A retreat is a time for recreation, reflection and reunion. Students often take part in different activities to help them
            develop their physical, social and team building skills. However the major focus of retreat is on spirituality,
            with students and teachers sharing liturgies, group discussions and individual reflections. The experience is
            overwhelmingly positive, with students and staff gaining new insights about themselves and each other.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

